<h1 itemprop="headline" class="wd-jnl-art-title">High-resolution x-ray diffraction of epitaxial bismuth chalcogenide topological insulator layers<SUP>*</SUP> </h1>

<p class="mb-0">
	<span data-authors="">
		<span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">V Holý</span><sup>1</sup></span>, <span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">D Kriegner</span><sup>1</sup></span>, <span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">H Steiner</span><sup>2</sup></span>, <span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">J Stangl</span><sup>2</sup></span>, <span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">G Bauer</span><sup>2</sup></span> and <span xmlns:m="http://ns.iop.org/namespaces/meta" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" class="nowrap"><span itemprop="name">G Springholz</span><sup>2</sup></span></span>
</p>

<p class="small" itemprop="isPartOf" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/PublicationIssue">
	<!--Article Breadcrumb Tile Start-->
<span class="wd-jnl-art-pub-date">Published 2 February 2017</span> &bull; <!-- Start Copyright-->
    <span itemprop="copyrightHolder" class="wd-jnl-art-copyright">
