ara K and Matsumoto T 1979 <I>Acta Cryst.</I> B <B>35</B> 147</cite><p class="mb-0"><a class="mr-2" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1107/S0567740879002788" title="Crossref">Crossref</a><a class="mr-2" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Yamana+K%2C+Kihara+K+and+Matsumoto+T+1979+Acta+Cryst.+B+35+147" title="Google Scholar">Google Scholar</a><a class="mr-2" title="Get it!@MST" onclick="window.open('http://UM9MH3KU7S.search.serialssolutions.com?sid=IOPP%3Ajnl_ref&id=doi%3A10.1107%2FS0567740879002788&genre=article&date=1979&aulast=Yamana&aufirst=K&issn=0108-7681&volume=35&spage=147&stitle=Acta+Cryst.','SFXmenu','location=no,status=yes,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,width=460,height=420'); return false;" href="http://UM9MH3KU7S.search.serialssolutions.com?sid=IOPP%3Ajnl_ref&id=doi%3A10.1107%2FS0567740879002788&genre=article&date=1979&aulast=Yamana&aufirst=K&issn=0108-7681&volume=35&spage=147&stitle=Acta+Cryst."> <img border="0" alt="Get it!@MST" src="http://library.mst.edu/media/campussupport/library/images/sersol_button_18x90.jpg"/> </a></p></div></li><li data-reference class="indices-list"><a class="indices-id" id="ansnaa5953bib005" name="ansnaa5953bib005" href="#fnref-ansnaa5953bib005">[5]</a><div class="indices-content"><cite>Massalski T B and Okamoto H 1996 <I>Binary Alloy Phase Diagrams</I> (Metals Park: ASM International)</cite><p class="mb-0"><a class="mr-2" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Massalski+T+B+and+Okamoto+H+1996+Binary+Alloy+Phase+Diagrams+%28Metals+Park%3A+ASM+International%29" title="Google Scholar">Google Scholar</a><a class="mr-2" title="Get it!@MST" onclick="window.open('http://UM9MH3KU7S.search.serialssolutions.com?sid=IOPP%3Ajnl_ref&genre=bookitem&date=1996&aulast=Massalski&aufirst=T+B+and+Okamoto+H&title=Binary+Alloy+Phase+Diagrams','SFXmenu','location=no,status=yes,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,width=460,height=420'); return false;" href="http://UM9MH3KU7S.search.serialssolutions.com?sid=IOPP%3Ajnl_ref&genre=book